section.title: Working with Aisec
section.desc: Being a sole developer working for an international company can be a strenuous task. However, AISEC did a great job towards smoothing out the whole remote experience by holding continuous sessions. Not just that, the international and the professional exposure that I gained during this internship proved to be quite useful during my career journey
